00:36:12.580 --> 00:36:14.490
what the sky was, what the weather was.

00:36:14.490 --> 00:36:17.480
All this detail of tracing a journey

00:36:17.480 --> 00:36:20.023
and trying to retrace a footstep.

00:36:21.900 --> 00:36:25.870
And then the priest
