Sits down, see someone raking leaves.

00:36:35.690 --> 00:36:38.137
Asks the person who's raking leaves,

00:36:38.137 --> 00:36:40.377
"What happened in this place?"

00:36:43.840 --> 00:36:45.763
That's part one of the play.

00:36:47.260 --> 00:36:49.400
Part two of the play

00:36:49.400 --> 00:36:53.940
