00:38:51.420 --> 00:38:52.930
there's a formal practice of

00:38:52.930 --> 00:38:55.640
when somebody leaves the world in pain,

00:38:55.640 --> 00:38:58.873
when someone leaves the world
in terrible circumstances,

00:39:00.310 --> 00:39:02.510
you make a ceremony for their spirit

00:39:02.510 --> 00:39:05.450
one year after their death

00:39:05.450 --> 00:39:08.040
and three years after their death,

00:39:08.040 --> 00:39:12.290
because nobody wants angry
spirits and hurt spirits

00:39:12.290 --> 00:39:15.343
wandering around because
it's terrible for everyone.

00:39:16.600 --> 00:39:19.260
And you create a ceremony
to call back the spirit

00:39:19.260 --> 00:39:21.977
of the person who's gone and say,

00:39:21.977 --> 00:39:24.907
"You died horribly, and we know that,

00:39:24.907 --> 00:39:27.620
"and we have to acknowledge your sadness."

00:39:27.620 --> 00:39:29.700
We have to acknowledge the injustice,

00:39:29.700 --> 00:39:31.270
we have to acknowledge all the things

00:39:31.270 --> 00:39:33.470
that were not acknowledged
in your lifetime.

00:39:34.890 --> 00:39:37.253
We have to let you know, we remember you,

00:39:38.160 --> 00:39:42.823
and we want to make
good what was very bad.

00:39:43.690 --> 00:39:46.240
We want to make just what was unjust.

00:39:46.240 --> 00:39:48.110
We wanna offer you the compassion

00:39:48.110 --> 00:39:49.910
and love that you did not feel then,

00:39:50.870 --> 00:39:52.653
and we're gonna create a ceremony.

00:39:55.260 --> 00:39:57.610
And of course the beginning of theater,

00:39:57.610 --> 00:40:00.170
the invention of the performing arts

00:40:00.170 --> 00:40:03.453
in most cultures is
performing for the dead,

00:40:04.670 --> 00:40:07.250
is actually the reason we perform

00:40:07.250 --> 00:40:09.393
is to tell the dead we remember them,

00:40:10.440 --> 00:40:14.273
to ask them to remember us kindly,

00:40:15.370 --> 00:40:18.070
better than we deserve to be remembered,

00:40:18.070 --> 00:40:20.290
ask them to favor us,

00:40:20.290 --> 00:40:23.030
and to somehow put back into balance

00:40:23.030 --> 00:40:25.600
something that is deeply out of balance.

00:40:25.600 --> 00:40:27.380
And we can't live another day

00:40:28.390 --> 00:40:30.733
with a memory of what was wrong.

00:40:32.490 --> 00:40:35.230
This play begins, is that ceremony,

